* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|en|/ˈʃaʊlɔŋbaʊ/}} or {{IPA|en|/ʃaʊlɔŋˈbaʊ/}}, ''{{smallcaps|shao}}-long-bao''
===Noun===
{{en-noun|xiaolongbao}}
# {{lb|en|Chinese cuisine}} A [[type]] of [[dumpling]] or [[steamed]] [[bun]] (''[[baozi]]'') [[associate]]d with [[eastern]] [[China]], [[particularly]] [[Nanxiang]] near [[Shanghai]].
